text: Carl Edwards (born 14 September 1963) is a British equestrian. He competed in two events at the 2000 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1963 births Category:Living people Category:British male equestrians Category:Olympic equestrians of Great Britain Category:Equestrians at the 2000 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
